{"tid":1669644,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"ʕ.ω.ʔ 市民一窩蜂幫襯黃店 無法解決問題","createTime":"2019-10-22T16:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T18:31:18.000Z","uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1909160273e84aee21c0188f40855432133fcf41","tid":1669644,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/1080/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/090651_2565a15623e1743eb9810a88c4d568af.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/1080/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/090709_6fa38e0a946fc6389ffc15694b15200e.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要鼓勵同路人 最理想嘅心態<br />\n應該係一有機會就幫襯<strong>良心店鋪</strong><br />\n而個別日子就強調爆買<br />\n咁先最幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>地圖</strong></span><br />\n【終極整合】黃藍商戶地圖 (持續更新中)<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">推薦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/9VZdBBxQrhWJSTYA7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F9VZdBBxQrhWJSTYA7&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=fb653f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/9VZdBBxQrhWJSTYA7</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsGap<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gotcha.hk.map\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.gotcha.hk.map&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=20894749\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gotcha.hk.map</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>好文分享</strong><br />\n【心理戰】立即停用藍黃陣營之分<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507207\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507207</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>討論</strong><br />\n另外大家覺得有裝支那寶、<br />\nWe7皮嘅「黃店」應否幫襯？<br />\n黨鐵範圍、黨鐵商場內嘅「黃店」又點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d5b67f597627c5e8ce6ec33579428d9f83a4cd","tid":1669644,"uid":16